21AudioSendStream::Stats::Stats() = default;
22AudioSendStream::Stats::~Stats() = default;
23
24AudioSendStream::Config::Config(Transport* send_transport)
25 : send_transport(send_transport) {}
26
27AudioSendStream::Config::~Config() = default;
28
29std::string AudioSendStream::Config::ToString() const {
30 rtc::StringBuilder ss;
31 ss << "{rtp: " << rtp.ToString();
32 ss << ", rtcp_report_interval_ms: " << rtcp_report_interval_ms;
33 ss << ", send_transport: " << (send_transport ? "(Transport)" : "null");
34 ss << ", min_bitrate_bps: " << min_bitrate_bps;
35 ss << ", max_bitrate_bps: " << max_bitrate_bps;
36 ss << ", has audio_network_adaptor_config: "
37 << (audio_network_adaptor_config ? "true" : "false");
38 ss << ", has_dscp: " << (has_dscp ? "true" : "false");
39 ss << ", send_codec_spec: "
40 << (send_codec_spec ? send_codec_spec->ToString() : "<unset>");
41 ss << "}";
42 return ss.Release();
43}
44
45AudioSendStream::Config::Rtp::Rtp() = default;
46
47AudioSendStream::Config::Rtp::~Rtp() = default;
48
49std::string AudioSendStream::Config::Rtp::ToString() const {
50 char buf[1024];
51 rtc::SimpleStringBuilder ss(buf);
52 ss << "{ssrc: " << ssrc;
53 if (!rid.empty()) {
54 ss << ", rid: " << rid;
55 }
56 if (!mid.empty()) {
57 ss << ", mid: " << mid;
58 }
59 ss << ", extmap-allow-mixed: " << (extmap_allow_mixed ? "true" : "false");
60 ss << ", extensions: [";
61 for (size_t i = 0; i < extensions.size(); ++i) {
62 ss << extensions[i].ToString();
63 if (i != extensions.size() - 1) {
64 ss << ", ";
65 }
66 }
67 ss << ']';
68 ss << ", c_name: " << c_name;
69 ss << '}';
70 return ss.str();
71}
72
73AudioSendStream::Config::SendCodecSpec::SendCodecSpec(
74 int payload_type,
75 const SdpAudioFormat& format)
76 : payload_type(payload_type), format(format) {}
77AudioSendStream::Config::SendCodecSpec::~SendCodecSpec() = default;
78
79std::string AudioSendStream::Config::SendCodecSpec::ToString() const {
80 char buf[1024];
81 rtc::SimpleStringBuilder ss(buf);
82 ss << "{nack_enabled: " << (nack_enabled ? "true" : "false");
83 ss << ", transport_cc_enabled: " << (transport_cc_enabled ? "true" : "false");
84 ss << ", cng_payload_type: "
85 << (cng_payload_type ? rtc::ToString(*cng_payload_type) : "<unset>");
86 ss << ", red_payload_type: "
87 << (red_payload_type ? rtc::ToString(*red_payload_type) : "<unset>");
88 ss << ", payload_type: " << payload_type;
89 ss << ", format: " << rtc::ToString(format);
90 ss << '}';
91 return ss.str();
92}
93
94bool AudioSendStream::Config::SendCodecSpec::operator==(
95 const AudioSendStream::Config::SendCodecSpec& rhs) const {
96 if (nack_enabled == rhs.nack_enabled &&
97 transport_cc_enabled == rhs.transport_cc_enabled &&
98 cng_payload_type == rhs.cng_payload_type &&
99 red_payload_type == rhs.red_payload_type &&
100 payload_type == rhs.payload_type && format == rhs.format &&
101 target_bitrate_bps == rhs.target_bitrate_bps) {
102 return true;
103 }
104 return false;
105}
